snippet.title: 'Midnight Scenes' Trailer. A short game by Octavi Navarro
snippet.description:
I made a short adventure game! :D
Get it for free on itch.io:
https://octavinavarro.itch.io/midnight-scenes-the-highway

I hope you enjoy it!! :)

If you enjoyed this game and would like to help on the creation of future titles, please consider your support on Patreon:

https://www.patreon.com/octavinavarro

Every little bit helps! :)

And don't forget to subscribe to the channel for more news and videos!!! :)

Pixel Art illustrations by Octavi Navarro. 2014-2017.
http://www.octavinavarro.com

Prints of my works are for sale here: http://www.redbubble.com/people/pixelshuh

Also, you can follow me on:
Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/OctaviNavarro
Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/octavinavarroAG
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/octavi_navarro
